Description: Lelu shell for Revenant OS - forked Cinnamon core
 Core binary + JavaScript shell tree of the Lelu desktop, a fork of
 upstream linuxmint/Cinnamon pinned at 6.4.6. Installs to /opt/lelu-shell/
 for alongside-install with stock cinnamon; does not disturb the default
 session.
 .
 Phase 4b release - unchanged-baseline packaging. Shell functionality
 equals upstream Cinnamon 6.4.6; Lelu visual overrides come from the
 revenant-theme-lelu-cinnamon package at runtime. Per-element rewrites
 (panel, menu, notifications, overlays) land in subsequent Phase 5 commits
 on the revenant/v0.1 branch.
 .
 Auxiliary Cinnamon tools (cinnamon-settings, cinnamon-menu-editor,
 cinnamon-screensaver-lock-dialog, cinnamon-desktop-editor) are NOT
 shipped by this package. Operators use the corresponding stock Mint
 packages for system configuration until those tools are ported forward.
